[
    {
        "content": "<p>If I was to define e.g. <code>let x := 37</code>, is there a tactic that would change <code>37</code> to <code>x</code> in the goal?</p>",
        "id": 479728525,
        "sender_full_name": "Duncan Skahan",
        "timestamp": 1730308062
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Does <code>change x to 37</code> work? That would be my guess</p>",
        "id": 479728700,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1730308112
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes. That looks useful.</p>",
        "id": 479729209,
        "sender_full_name": "Duncan Skahan",
        "timestamp": 1730308275
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can probably also use <code>set</code> instead of <code>let</code> (and <code>set ... with h</code> to get the equality as an extra assumption).</p>",
        "id": 479729402,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1730308348
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">37</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">37</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">refold_let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- ⊢ x = a</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 479729503,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1730308383
    },
    {
